high_descs: Turn to the right and go to the edge of the bath tub near the faucet.
Pick up the candle on the corner of the tub.
Turn to your right and head toward the door, then turn left and go to the shelf to the left of the toilet.
Put the candle on the bottom shelf.
Turn to your left and go to the counter in the corner to your left.
Pick up the candle on the counter.
Go back to the shelf to the left of the toilet.
Put the candle on the bottom shelf to the right of the first candle.
anns.task_desc: Put two candles on the shelf to the left of the toilet.

high_descs: Turn right and go to the corner of the tub to the right of the drain.
Pick up the candle on the corner of the tub.
Turn right, go to the door, then turn left to the dark gray shelves.
Put the candle at the edge of the dark gray bottom shelf.
Turn left, go to the drawer stand on the left side next to the garbage can.
Take the candle on top of the drawer stand.
Turn around, go the dark gray shelves to the left.
Put the candle to the right of the other candle on the dark gray bottom shelf.
anns.task_desc: Put the candles on a shelf.

high_descs: Turn right face the top of the tub.
Pick up the candle off the tub.
Turn around a walk forward a couple steps, then turn left and face the left cabinet.
Place the candle on the bottom shelf of the fixture.
Turn left and walk to the cabinet to the far left.
Pick up the candle on the cabinet.
Turn around and walk back to the first cabinet on the left.
Place the candle on the bottom shelf to the left of the first candle.
anns.task_desc: Place two candles on a shelf.
